{"tid":1653009,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[連仔入 其他人推] [L牌方案] 另一個要人登出嘅方法","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T06:05:05.000Z","uid":196918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3a47294071f9574f62349c85e70a6d3a34d37c","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"連仔你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直有人推「force logout」，但唔知係不能定不為，你一直都冇做到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「不為」嘅原因我諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁我假設係「不能」嘅前提下提供以下方案。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時間X</span>為你<span style=\"color: orange;\">設立並公佈呢個方案嘅日期</span> <br />\n或<span style=\"color: orange;\">日後再重新推行該方案日期</span><br />\n如果用戶在<span style=\"color: red;\">時間X</span><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">之後沒有</span></strong>登出再登入過，就會獲到「L牌」（因為關login, logout事，暫停其名為L牌）<br />\n<br />\nL牌用戶嘅限制在短時間內應與P牌睇齊，檢討後長線黎講限制應比P牌<span style=\"color: red;\">更多</span>，因為P牌或可能有新用戶但<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>L牌只會係忘記帳戶密碼嘅人同被盜用帳戶嘅人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講咩一向冇存下用戶嘅登出登入時間，呢個方法係你今日開始新加column係DB都做到嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望連仔你睇到可以覆一覆<br />\n就算做唔到都提供下「不能」或者「不為」嘅原因<br />\n睇唔明都可以講句，我寫埋pseudo code比你都ok<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復連登，從登出做起</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e8502a3ad94a9be1697d7f0b6b25baa7316528","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:00:06.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fead8ccc3b048f1c3ddfc19b1df55c5152afaaa","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"連仔入黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c2cc510173f6891cb99112a498586ffd3d4c24","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:01:47.000Z","msg":"連登死啦 救下連登啦"},{"pid":"d7eb05928988663158c2cf9ee5f81b9b9131a49b","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519be997733ceab2f6df4312c9fa89ce25c69acf","tid":1653009,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"226438088656aefec7174ad39f307a6a98a7e658","tid":1653009,"uid":19095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"2bb990822e8d92c24ae605695360c6203c4af4cb","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:09:24.000Z","msg":"推啊 繼續推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f97cbe3b7cc32372c27f1ada765c53718b378f","tid":1653009,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:09:52.000Z","msg":"叫曬全家入黎推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3ad2f3f708d2a96fe502757556d9d8421ea15b","tid":1653009,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep